### Core Entry Points:

- `src/main.js` — orchestrates console startup, backend selection, API wiring
- `console.html` — main console page (Three.js backend)
- `babylon_console.html` — console page using Babylon.js backend
- `cart-runner.html` — lightweight runner used by `nova64 dev` CLI command
- `vite.config.js` — build configuration

### Development Tools:

- **Real-time Editor**: in-browser sprite and material editing
- **Performance Monitor**: FPS, triangle count, memory analytics
- **Debug Panel** (F9): scene graph, camera, lights, console log
- **Build Pipeline**: `pnpm build` → `vite build` + `scripts/postbuild.js`
